# Approach
We can divide it into 4 parts:-
    1.Find if the number is palindrome or not.
    2.Find if the number is prime or not.
    3.If it satisfy both prime and palindrome than we return n.
    4.Else while(true) -> If n satisfy both prime and Palindrome -> return n. Else -> n++.
